---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const updated = '2026-04-17';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy policy"
  description="How AISO Group handles information submitted through aiso-group.com. Minimal, EU-based, and explicit."
>
  <section class="bg-[#0A1628] text-white">
    <div class="container-aiso section !py-16 md:!py-24">
      <span class="kicker kicker-on-dark mb-4 block">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="h1 !text-white">Privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-4">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="container-aiso section">
      <div class="article-body">
        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          AISO Group is a brand operated by Precious Episode LDA, a company registered in Portugal (NIF PT516578506). The group is the parent of four specialist companies: AISO Hub, AISO Dev, AISO Buzz, and AISO Learn.
        </p>

        <h2>What we collect</h2>
        <p>On <strong>aiso-group.com</strong> we collect only what you hand us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact form.</strong> Name, company, message, and (optionally) email. Used to reply to you and route you to the right sibling brand.</li>
          <li><strong>Email.</strong> If you write to <a href="mailto:hello@aiso-group.com">hello@aiso-group.com</a>, we keep the thread in our mailbox.</li>
          <li><strong>Server logs.</strong> Cloudflare edge logs (IP, user agent, path) for security and debugging. Retained up to 30 days.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>No tracking cookies. No ad pixels. No analytics that identify you personally.</p>

        <h2>What we do with it</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Reply to your inbound.</li>
          <li>Route you to Hub, Dev, or Buzz internally.</li>
          <li>Keep a minimal record of our correspondence.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell or rent your data to anyone. Ever.</p>

        <h2>Who sees your data</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Greg Stoos</strong> (founder) and the triage operator.</li>
          <li>The specialist team at the sibling brand we route you to, if we route you.</li>
          <li><strong>Processors:</strong> Cloudflare (hosting), Resend (email delivery), Google Workspace (mailbox). All GDPR-compliant.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>
          You can ask for a copy of your data, ask us to correct it, or ask us to delete it. Email <a href="mailto:hello@aiso-group.com">hello@aiso-group.com</a> with "GDPR request" in the subject. We reply within 30 days.
        </p>

        <h2>Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Contact-form entries: kept for 24 months unless you ask us to delete them sooner, or unless our correspondence continues.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>
          We update this page when the practice changes. The "last updated" date above is the source of truth.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Precious Episode LDA</strong><br />
          Lisbon, Portugal · NIF PT516578506<br />
          <a href="mailto:hello@aiso-group.com">hello@aiso-group.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
